answer: The document published by the Ministry of Education of the People's Republic of China on February 21, 2020, is not explicitly named as "高等教育专业设置与调整办法" (Regulations on the Setting and Adjustment of Higher Education Programs) in the search results. Instead, the closest similar document published in 2023 is "教育部等五部门印发《普通高等教育学科专业设置调整优化改革方案》" (The Ministry of Education and Five Other Departments Issued the Notice on the Adjustment and Optimization of the Academic Programs of Ordinary Higher Education).
